sourceQuery: select * from "data-products".data_product_records where created_at >= TO_TIMESTAMP(?, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') and created_at <= TO_TIMESTAMP(?, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')
destQuery: select * FROM data_product_records WHERE created_at >= TO_TIMESTAMP($1, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') AND created_at <= TO_TIMESTAMP($2, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')
